Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 10:52:55 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?Phase=209:=20workbench=20shell=20=E2=80=94=20st?=
 =?UTF-8?q?rip=20Copilot,=20demo=20header,=20indigo=20+=20compact=20themin?=
 =?UTF-8?q?g?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Strip Copilot UI: chat.disableAIFeatures + chat.agentsControl.enabled
  in krtChrome defaults, plus surgical deletions of two upstream title-
  bar menu registrations (Open in Agents in openInAgentsAction.ts; Chat
  submenu in agentSessionsExperiments.contribution.ts).
- PR pane header gains right-aligned action cluster: Refresh (re-fetch
  via IPullRequestProvider.getPullRequest) + Open on GitHub (external
  via IOpenerService). State pill moves inline next to the title.
- Indigo + compact density become defaults via --krt-* design tokens on
  the workbench root + workbench.editor.tabSizing/editor.fontSize/
  workbench.panel.defaultLocation: 'right' config overrides.
- Add github.com (+ subdomains, github.io, githubusercontent.com) to
  product.json's linkProtectionTrustedDomains so external GitHub links
  open without the trust-prompt dialog.

Steps 4 (functional rail), 5 (separate Code/PR editor groups), and 8
(editor-view LSP parity) deferred — they require the Phase 8.5/8.6
workspace registry which isn't in this branch and are big enough to
warrant their own patch series.
